    <h2>UI Colors</h2>
    <h3>Color Palette</h3>
    <p>The colors for the Robot interface are typically shades of blue and grays, with the exception of alerts. To keep the styles organized, variables in the <code>_base.scss</code> file contains color information. There are standard defaults, but the vital color information is organized by sections of the UI within the .scss file. </p>

    <h4>Primary Palette</h4>

    <p>These are the colors which are crucial to the first impression. At a glance, these are the most recognizable and are necessary for a consistent experience throughout the entire application. Future enhancements should use and build upon what was created with this palette.</p>

