    <h4>Secondary Palette</h4>

    <p>Lists in Robot often provide key visual elements making it easy to see the status. Although they are smaller, the color is very important to accurately represent what needs to be communicated. Often these are shown as circles.</p>

    <p>There is a class of <code>.schedule-module</code> that needs to be included. Nested within that class, are icon classes that give the colored styling of the dots.</p>

    <!-- start example -->

    <div class="datatable grid panel ui-page">
        <div id="datatable-content" class="panel-content">
